snippet.textDisplay: I loved the way Atif Aslam presented the names it’s really an epic. But the post production must be scrutinized as they animated the names connected to his hands which sometimes takes them at lower positions as well one towards his feet. They could choose white color for names which is the color of Noor of Allah rather they chosen Amber color which represents fire. I hope they may be corrected in future.
